    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "it's all gone. years of work, all based on a fundamental error i didn't see. i'm not just a failure, i'm a fraud. there's no point in even trying to fix it because there's nothing left of me to fix. i feel like i've just been playing a part that doesn't exist anymore.",
